{"tid":585780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB洩密率先報喜 湯盈盈再懷孕佗第3胎","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T18:19:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9a3b680094e19a8ded15672a764b21ae2fd880","tid":585780,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】湯盈盈婚後為老公錢嘉樂誕下兩個可愛女兒，一直有傳盈盈想生第3胎追B仔，去年11月就有傳盈盈懷有第3胎，嘉樂仔仲買了港島區半山豪宅，讓盈盈退出娛樂圈後有個更安逸的家，專心相夫教子；當時盈盈第一時間否認再佗B，話等兩個女大一點才考慮，即是不排除再生啦！<br />\n<br />\n今早TVB臉書專頁，就上載盈盈同4歲大女錢凱晴（Alyssa）去做親子手作片段，原本標題是【恭喜 湯盈盈 再度懷孕！】，不過之後這標題已刪掉，內文都刪除「恭喜盈盈又有喜啊！」這一句，但卻保留「大家姐嘅囡囡Alyssa（錢凱晴）同Kassidy（錢凱琪）應該都好期待有其他兄弟姊妹喇」，未知是否未夠3個月不能公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/szF6k4p2MIKb6fqbw12gtw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180308f163329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FszF6k4p2MIKb6fqbw12gtw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180308f163329.jpg&h=c6198064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/tvb%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%A0%B1%E5%96%9C-%E6%B9%AF%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E5%86%8D%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E4%BD%97%E7%AC%AC3%E8%83%8E-081200788.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2Ftvb%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2596%259C-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E7%259B%2588%25E7%259B%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E4%25BD%2597%25E7%25AC%25AC3%25E8%2583%258E-081200788.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=64d551fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/tvb%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%A0%B1%E5%96%9C-%E6%B9%AF%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E5%86%8D%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E4%BD%97%E7%AC%AC3%E8%83%8E-081200788.html</a>"},{"pid":"3f2b7e